<table class="data-table">
  <thead><tr><th>Sub-concern</th><th>Already-ruled home</th><th>Evidence (real tree)</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>offline queue + replay</td><td><strong>webreliability</strong> outbox + the <code>mutation</code> intent (apply/reconcile/rollback)</td><td><code>storage.json:4</code>; <code>mutation.json:6</code> (#1395); running queue = <code>resource-action</code>'s <code>withOptimisticMutation</code></td></tr>
